{"tid":1928804,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"周浩鼎譴責王進洋拒協助支持23條立法市民　做法卑劣","createTime":"2020-03-16T14:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T04:32:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"babb3b76c0b5243a71cf506cec0887d701cce99b","tid":1928804,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:53:11.000Z","msg":"民建聯立法會議員周浩鼎譴責東涌區議員王進洋，批評王進洋表明拒絕協助支持《基本法》23條立法的市民，要求王進洋收回言論及道歉。<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎形容，有關做法有如「順我者昌，逆我者亡」，以政治取態帶頭歧視，非常卑劣，污衊民選議員的公職崗位。周浩鼎又指，早前公民黨深水埗區議員劉家衡的辦事處外，貼上「藍絲與狗不得內進」的告示，製造歧視氛圍，要求公民黨交代如何看待及處理。<br />\n<br />\n王進洋早前於社交網站表示，基於良知，拒絕接受所有支持《基本法》23條立法的市民的求助，直到永遠。王進洋於去年底區議會選舉，於東涌南選區擊敗周浩鼎當選。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514860-20200316.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514860-20200316.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=e7ef6ac0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514860-20200316.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6abc6f05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514860-20200316.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ecbf0ab96af2cb2ba01e7166cafba5eeda691404","tid":1928804,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:54:25.000Z","msg":"On9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5696b1f7191bc3972dabac494a9dee63d20a7903","tid":1928804,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"藍絲: 絲帶<br />\n狗: 動物<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"05188dccf4eaf0e70e07b1451a0bc79ecd1df822","tid":1928804,"uid":37413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:58:07.000Z","msg":"手下敗將收聲，有本事下屆攞番個位"},{"pid":"084bea5a156799c6c7b5baff9388b1dd6b8ff35d","tid":1928804,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit